          <text><![CDATA[<p><strong>Restoring Rural Residencies Act of 2016</strong></p> <p>This bill amends title XVIII (Medicare) of the Social Security Act to require the Centers for Medicare &amp; Medicaid Services to reimburse medical residency training programs under Medicare for certain graduate medical education&nbsp;costs associated with&nbsp;resident time spent in rural community hospitals known as "critical access hospitals." </p>]]></text>
